<H2 class="lh2">Lines of Business</H2>
<p style="margin: 9 0 3 0;"><b>Global Consumer & Small Business Banking</b></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 12 0;">GCSB provides products and services to help individuals, small businesses and middle-market companies realize their dreams. GCSB reaches over 33 million households across 29 states, and serves more than 1 in 4 U.S. households.</p>

<p style="margin: 9 0 3 0;"><b>Global Wealth & Investment Management</b></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 12 0;">GWIM provides wealth and investment management services to clients in the U.S. and globally. GWIM represents the largest Private Bank and the third largest bank-owned brokerage company in the country.</p>

<p style="margin: 9 0 3 0;"><b>Global Corporate & Investment Banking</b></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 12 0;">GCIB is a full-service, integrated commercial and investment bank with offices in more than 30 countries, serving clients in more than 150 countries. GCIB maintains a relationship with more than 97% of the Fortune 500 and nearly 2,000 institutional investors worldwide.</p>

<p style="margin: 9 0 3 0;"><b>Global Technology Service & Fulfillment</b></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 12 0;">GTS&F executes Bank of America customer, client and associate needs and requests through technology, systems and contact centers. GTS&F is comprised of more than 50,000 associates and oversees bankofamerica.com - the largest online banking platform in the world.</p>

<p style="margin: 9 0 3 0;"><b>Corporate Staff & Support</b></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 12 0;">Corporate Staff & Support provides support and functional expertise to Bank of America customers, clients, shareholders as well as associates representing all lines of business across the enterprise.</p>

